=E2=80=9CTruth always rests with the minority=2C=E2=80=9D the great Danish=
 philosopher S=C3=B8ren Kierkegaard wrote in his diary in 1846 as he conte=
mplated the individual vs. the crowd and why we conform (https://www.brain=
