mc_cid=3D584266f283&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) =2C =E2=80=9Cbecause the minority=
 is generally formed by those who really have an opinion=2C while the stre=
ngth of a majority is illusory=2C formed by the gangs who have no opinion.=
