p://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0143106503/bpnl-20?mc_cid=3D584266f283=
&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) (free ebook (http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/B=
01CTAYQ9E/bpnl-20?mc_cid=3D584266f283&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) | public library=
 (http://www.worldcat.org/title/walden-and-civil-disobedience-authoritativ=
