rief_results?mc_cid=3D584266f283&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) ).

http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0451532163/bpnl-20?mc_cid=3D584266f=
283&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]

Published in 1849 =E2=80=94 well before Thoreau=E2=80=99s vivid writings a=
bout the glory of nature (https://www.brainpickings.org/2015/09/16/thoreau=
-silence-conversation-walden/?mc_cid=3D584266f283&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) and=
